channel.title: Somthings wrong with advertisement place?
channel.description:
Hey everyone, im kinda new to forums.
I went to the status advertisement page thing. And i went to the bottum and registered my server.
And it said it would put it on there if it passed....and i noticed that someone that i dont know signed on my server so im guessing that was the guy that passes my server. And then i read at the bottum that the page updates so i waited for that, and it still wasnt there :( Any clue why? its 508 btw.....that isnt against the rules is it?
